node.text: Slavery in Libya by @louisthehippie  The truth maybe hard to swallow but who is it harder for? You or someone who's life is being sold. We must do something! No more ignoring, no more distractions, we must burst the bubble that separates us from the rest of the world. We are all part of one world and people are suffering. We are all worth the same and if one man is being sold for less than an iPhone then that shows how much we value the human race and ourselves. We are all worth more than this, you cannot put a price on a life. Let's join together, spread the message and end this hate. Love can save us, if you don't feel it, just know it and don't forget it. Repost @the_real_iman @maxwell
